= Change System Timezone =

To prevent package [https://gitlab.com/whonix/anon-apps-config anon-apps-config] from changing the timezone to UTC during upgrades, create either file <code>/etc/noutc</code> or <code>/usr/local/etc/noutc</code>. <ref>
https://gitlab.com/whonix/anon-apps-config/-/commit/85dcdaaeafe150a740949d5b8d167e6f0fa10c7d
</ref>

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo touch /etc/noutc
}}

<ref>
{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/etc/
}}

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo touch /usr/local/etc/noutc
}}
</ref>

